      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON TO AVOID (1) boasts a strong record this course with six wins and two minors from 12 tries. Scored by 2 lengths last time (22.94) in a Grade 5 over 400m at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. ENERGY TO BURN (4) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 5 lengths back in third (17.77) at this track in a Grade 2/3/4 over 305m. Deserves a win and gets his chance. DIRTY DASH (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (29.85) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Has a good record here including nine wins. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Has ability and can atone. COMPTON LIZZIE (5) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.",
